{
  "schema_version": "2026-04-26.v1",
  "purpose": "Machine-readable unit activation templates for UniWar engine and bot code.",
  "notes": [
    "Profiles describe activation structure, not combat resolution.",
    "Numeric mobility values are usually taken from the unit definition file via fields like surface, underground, and after attack.",
    "Some units still have unresolved public documentation quirks, especially Marauder action splitting and Battery move-field interpretation."
  ],
  "profiles": {
